treb: An application that allows you to run mobile or small web pages in your system notification area. 
treb:
treb: You can download pre-configured packages (treb instances) that allows you to set up some of the 
treb: pages quickly, including Google Plus, Facebook, Twitter, Google Tasks, Dictionary.com, 
treb: Google Calendar etc.
treb:
treb: Homepage of project: http://treb.sf.net/
treb: More information about treb at author's blog post:
treb:  http://yyjhao.wordpress.com/2011/08/13/run-google-task-google-plus-in-your-system-tray-and-more/
treb:
treb: Packaged by MiRacLe.RPZ <miracle@rpz.name>